io.vertx.ext.shell.command

Interface CommandRegistry

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CommandResolver

    public interface CommandRegistry
extends CommandResolver
    A registry that contains the commands known by a shell.

    It is a mutable command resolver.

    Author:
    Julien Viet
